d.script:
--[[
4.8
I18nGenerator {
    "lvlsub_4_8_010_the_time_has_come",
    "lvlsub_4_8_020_it_is_like_stakey",
    "lvlsub_4_8_030_head_is_completely",
    "lvlsub_4_8_040_all_parts_of_body",
    "lvlsub_4_8_050_i_advise_you",
    "lvlsub_4_8_060_the_mobchain",
    "lvlsub_4_8_070_good_job",
    "lvlsub_4_8_080_i_want_to_congratulate",
    "lvlsub_4_8_090_dont_stay_here"
}
--]]
local TAG = "4.8.lua: "

dofile("scripts/utils/tutorial.lua")

local i18n = function() return managers.LocaleManager.i18n end
local sm = function() return SP._graphics.storylineMessages end
local st = function() return SP._graphics.subtitles end

local BOSS_WAVE_NUMBER = 50
local forceSubtitles = false

local tut

addEventHandler("SystemPostSetup", function()
    forceSubtitles = managers.BasicLevelManager:getLevel("4.8").maxReachedWave >= BOSS_WAVE_NUMBER or SP.gameState.gameIsContinued
    tut:start()

    SP.gameState.listeners:add(luajava.createProxy(GNS .. "systems.GameStateSystem$GameStateSystemListener", {
        realUpdate = function(deltaTime)
            tut:update(deltaTime)
        end,

        affectsGameState = function() return true end, -- Заставляем сериализовать слушателя
        getConstantId = function() return 50 end
    }))
end)

tut = tutorial:new({
    {
        check = function()
            return SP.wave:getCompletedWavesCount() >= BOSS_WAVE_NUMBER
        end,
        start = function()
            tut:delay(2, function()
                if SP._graphics ~= nil then
                    local messages = {
                        tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_010_the_time_has_come"),
                        tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_020_it_is_like_stakey"),
                        tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_030_head_is_completely"),
                        tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_040_all_parts_of_body"),
                        tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_050_i_advise_you")
                    }

                    if forceSubtitles then
                        -- subtitles
                        st():schedule(messages, 0, 5)
                    else
                        -- story line messages
                        sm():queue(messages)
                    end
                end

                tut:condition(function() return SP.wave.wave ~= nil and SP.wave.wave.waveNumber >= BOSS_WAVE_NUMBER - 3 end, function()
                    if SP._graphics ~= nil then
                        st():add(tut.ENSOR_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_060_the_mobchain"))
                    end
                end)
            end)
        end,
        done = function()
            if SP._graphics ~= nil then
                local messages = {
                    tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_070_good_job"),
                    tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_080_i_want_to_congratulate"),
                    tut.ADVINAS_TAG .. " " .. i18n():get("lvlsub_4_8_090_dont_stay_here")
                }
                if forceSubtitles then
                    st():schedule(messages, 1, 5)
                else
                    sm():queue(messages)
                end
            end
        end
    }
})
tut._noSyncCheck = true
